<strong>The company:</strong></p>
<p>
SocialChorus is the leading social word-of-mouth marketing solution for the brands that people love. SocialChorus customers, including dozens of Fortune 500 brands, inspire social advocates to deliver millions of trusted, social endorsements across all social channels.</p>
<p>
It&#39;s a great time to join SocialChorus. We have proven that 2-5% of a brand&rsquo;s social audience generates most of the social engagement, endorsement and referral; our solution powers those superfans to make it happen. Over 30 Fortune 500 brands have already implemented SocialChorus-powered marketing programs.</p>
