Working knowledge of social media marketing</li>
<li>
Direct or alliance sales experience selling enterprise solutions</li>
<li>
Exceptional communication, presentation and negotiation skills</li>
<li>
Self-starter with great time management skills</li>
<li>
Able to develop and nurture key relationships with executives and sales teams</li>
<li>
Must execute program objectives both as a thought leader and individual contributor in a fast-paced, rapidly changing environment.</li>
<li>
Willingness to travel</li>
</ul>
<p>
